    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor: I was disappointed that the article on Saratoga did not mention the Inn at Saratoga, which is directly across from the Holiday Inn. It has an excellent dining room and the staff is most helpful. The environment is restored Victorian and very comfortable. KATHRYN COHEN Tonawanda, N.Y.</p>
      </block>
